  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed; structured level evidence is provided for 12 factors. The model form factor was evaluated through an extensive qualitative expert-panel review and is documented via narrative rationale. Overall assessment concludes sufficient credibility for the intended use.",
